{% layout "layouts/base.liquid" %}
{% block title %}Frame — Cubito UI Docs{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
<article class="flow">

  <header class="padding-y-m margin-y-m" style="border-block-end: 1px solid var(--color-neutral-200);">
    <nav aria-label="Breadcrumb" class="breadcrumb">
      <ol>
        <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="/layouts/">Layouts</a></li>
        <li aria-current="page">Frame</li>
      </ol>
    </nav>
    <h1>Frame</h1>
    <p class="text-l color-neutral-600">Constrains media to a specific aspect ratio by cropping, so layout stays stable regardless of the source image or video dimensions.</p>
  </header>

  <section>
    <h2 class="heading-l">16:9</h2>
    <p>The default ratio is 16:9. Any content placed inside is cropped to fill the frame.</p>
    
    <div class="padding-m margin-y-m background-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200">
<div class="frame" style="max-width: 40rem;">
  <div style="background: #6366f1; width: 100%; height: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: #fff; font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 600;">
    16 : 9
  </div>
</div>
    </div>

    <details class="margin-y-s">
      <summary class="padding-s">Show code</summary>
      <pre class="padding-m background-neutral-900" style="overflow-x: auto;"><code>&lt;div class=&quot;frame&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 40rem;&quot;&gt;
  &lt;div style=&quot;background: #6366f1; width: 100%; height: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: #fff; font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 600;&quot;&gt;
    16 : 9
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre>
    </details>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2 class="heading-l">4:3 and 1:1</h2>
    <p>Override <code>--n</code> (width numerator) and <code>--d</code> (height denominator) inline to change the ratio.</p>
    
    <div class="padding-m margin-y-m background-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200">
<div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap;">
  <div style="flex: 1; min-width: 10rem;">
    <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: #6b7280; margin-block-end: 0.4rem;">4:3</p>
    <div class="frame" style="--n: 4; --d: 3;">
      <div style="background: #818cf8; width: 100%; height: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: #fff; font-weight: 600;">
        4 : 3
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="flex: 1; min-width: 10rem;">
    <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: #6b7280; margin-block-end: 0.4rem;">1:1 (square)</p>
    <div class="frame" style="--n: 1; --d: 1;">
      <div style="background: #a5b4fc; width: 100%; height: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: #fff; font-weight: 600;">
        1 : 1
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="flex: 1; min-width: 10rem;">
    <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: #6b7280; margin-block-end: 0.4rem;">2:3 (portrait)</p>
    <div class="frame" style="--n: 2; --d: 3;">
      <div style="background: #c7d2fe; width: 100%; height: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: 600;">
        2 : 3
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
    </div>

    <details class="margin-y-s">
      <summary class="padding-s">Show code</summary>
      <pre class="padding-m background-neutral-900" style="overflow-x: auto;"><code>&lt;div style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap;&quot;&gt;
  &lt;div style=&quot;flex: 1; min-width: 10rem;&quot;&gt;
    &lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 0.875rem; color: #6b7280; margin-block-end: 0.4rem;&quot;&gt;4:3&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;frame&quot; style=&quot;--n: 4; --d: 3;&quot;&gt;
      &lt;div style=&quot;background: #818cf8; width: 100%; height: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: #fff; font-weight: 600;&quot;&gt;
        4 : 3
      &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;

  &lt;div style=&quot;flex: 1; min-width: 10rem;&quot;&gt;
    &lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 0.875rem; color: #6b7280; margin-block-end: 0.4rem;&quot;&gt;1:1 (square)&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;frame&quot; style=&quot;--n: 1; --d: 1;&quot;&gt;
      &lt;div style=&quot;background: #a5b4fc; width: 100%; height: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: #fff; font-weight: 600;&quot;&gt;
        1 : 1
      &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;

  &lt;div style=&quot;flex: 1; min-width: 10rem;&quot;&gt;
    &lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 0.875rem; color: #6b7280; margin-block-end: 0.4rem;&quot;&gt;2:3 (portrait)&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;frame&quot; style=&quot;--n: 2; --d: 3;&quot;&gt;
      &lt;div style=&quot;background: #c7d2fe; width: 100%; height: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: 600;&quot;&gt;
        2 : 3
      &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre>
    </details>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2 class="heading-l">With img</h2>
    <p>The frame crops <code>&lt;img&gt;</code> and <code>&lt;video&gt;</code> children to fill using <code>object-fit: cover</code>. The image's natural dimensions do not matter.</p>
    
    <div class="padding-m margin-y-m background-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200">
<div class="frame" style="max-width: 32rem;">
  <img
    src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506905925346-21bda4d32df4?w=800&q=80"
    alt="Mountain landscape with snow-capped peaks and a clear blue lake"
  >
</div>
    </div>

    <details class="margin-y-s">
      <summary class="padding-s">Show code</summary>
      <pre class="padding-m background-neutral-900" style="overflow-x: auto;"><code>&lt;div class=&quot;frame&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 32rem;&quot;&gt;
  &lt;img
    src=&quot;https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506905925346-21bda4d32df4?w=800&amp;q=80&quot;
    alt=&quot;Mountain landscape with snow-capped peaks and a clear blue lake&quot;
  &gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre>
    </details>

    <div class="callout" data-variant="brand" role="note">
      <p>The frame uses <code>overflow: hidden</code> and <code>object-fit: cover</code> on child images and videos. Any content that overflows the aspect-ratio box is clipped.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2 class="heading-l">Tokens</h2>
    <table class="">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Token</th>
          <th>Default</th>
          <th>Description</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td><code>--n</code></td>
          <td><code>16</code></td>
          <td>Width numerator of the aspect ratio. Set inline to change ratio.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><code>--d</code></td>
          <td><code>9</code></td>
          <td>Height denominator of the aspect ratio. Set inline to change ratio.</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </section>

</article>
{% endblock %}
